Class: Moons

Moons

An api adapter that provides functions for accessing moon information via the universe ESI end points. You should not usually instantiate this directly as its constructor requires an internal api instance.

This is a function class so instances of Moons are functions and can be invoked directly, besides accessing its members. Its default function action is equivalent to get.

new Moons(agent)

Create a new Moons instance using the given agent.

Parameters:
Name Type Description
agent ESIAgent

The ESI agent

Methods

get(id)

Create a new Moon end point targeting the particular moon by id.

Parameters:
Name Type Description
id Number

The moon id
Returns:
Type
Moon
